name: Pachet muzical | Daniel Sadowski, Crimson Assault
description: Video Game Composer Daniel Sadowski delivers Edgy Action mixed with CRAZY FAT beats in this pulsating, exhilarating Music Pack.

name: Pachet muzical | Noisia, Sharpened
description: Dutch Electronic Trio Noisia brings a tough, cinematic feel with a unique blend of tradition and progression.

name: Pachet muzical | Robert Allaire, Insurgency
description: Music to crush your enemies see them driven before you from award winning composer Robert Allaire.

name: Pachet muzical | Sean Murray, A*D*8
description: De la compozitorul a două dintre cele mai mărețe jocuri de război din lume, vine o revărsare sonică, care va purta inamicii către Porțile Iadului!!

name: Pachet muzical | Feed Me, High Noon
description: Renowned dubstep Dj Feed Me, brings a western corral showdown into a modern electronic space.

name: Pachet muzical | Dren, Death's Head Demolition
description: From game music composer Dren, this cinematic, superhero-metal inspired music pack puts the 'ill' into KILL!

name: Pachet muzical | Austin Wintory, Desert Fire
description: Grammy nominated game composer Austin Wintory asks, why bother hunting your enemies when you can lure them in with a deadly, admittedly insane, tango?

name: Pachet muzical | Sasha, LNOE
description: Immerse yourself in this cinematic soundtrack full of soaring strings, pulsating melodies and driving drums from the world renowned DJ / Producer Sasha

name: Pachet muzical | Skog, Metal
description: A lesson in aggression from Metal producer, Skog.

name: Pachet muzical | Midnight Riders, All I Want for Christmas
description: „SĂRBĂTORI FERICITE, ******LOR!”\n -Midnight Riders

name: Pachet muzical | Matt Lange, IsoRhythm
description: Răsfață-ți simțurile auditive cu o colecție de atmosfere cinematice, întrerupte, cu ritmuri dure, creată de către Matt Lange, inovatorul și producătorul electronic.

name: Pachet muzical | Mateo Messina, For No Mankind
description: Own your enemies. Pure intensity by Grammy winning composer, Mateo Messina.

name: Pachet muzical | Artiști diverși, Hotline Miami
description: A multitude of electronic artists deliver brutal beats in this exhilarating Music Pack from the iconic Hotline Miami.

name: Pachet muzical | Daniel Sadowski, Total Domination
description: Composer Daniel Sadowski raises the bar with aggressive electronic beats, creative sound fx and an exhilarating, driving, futuristic vibe. \"Warning: Will cause a rise in adrenaline!\"

name: Pachet muzical | Damjan Mravunac, The Talos Principle
description: Composer Damjan Mravunac blends energetic cinematic grooves with epic choirs in this music pack featuring music from Croteam's critically acclaimed title \"The Talos Principle\".

name: Pachet muzical | Proxy, Battlepack
description: Russian Heavy Electronica Artist PROXY brings his own Unique heavy artillery to Counter Strike. Hybrid audio Weaponry fused with the finest studio technology makes this pack unique.

name: Pachet muzical | Ki:Theory, MOLOTOV
description: Artistul și interpretul de la TI4 DOTA, Ki:Theory aruncă BOMBE cu setul său mistuitor de rock electric într-un stil întunecat.

name: Pachet muzical | Troels Folmann, Uber Blasto Phone
description: Triumphant Blastophones combine with contemporary Uberpulse in this explosive collection by ultra award winning composer Troels Folmann.

name: Pachet muzical | Kelly Bailey, Hazardous Environments
description: Kelly Bailey, composer of Valve’s Half-Life series, creates an arsenal of apocalyptic new music inspired by the darker side of the Half-Life universe.

name: Pachet muzical | Skog, II-Headshot
description: Metal composer and producer Jocke Skog returns with an all new, hard hitting metal kit, turning the rest of the CS:GO Music Kits into something cute, warm and fuzzy. Now go become MVP so everyone can hear your awesomeness!

name: Pachet muzical | Daniel Sadowski, The 8-Bit Kit
description: Daniel Sadowski creates the first ever 8-bit Music Kit for Counter-Strike complete with authentic 8-bit sounds.

name: Pachet muzical | AWOLNATION, I Am
description: AWOLNATION Alternative Rocker AWOLNATION brings you a music kit for the ages. This kit is jam-packed with an eclectic selection of tunes and includes cuts from singles 'I Am' and multi-platinum hit 'Sail'.

name: Pachet muzical | Mord Fustang, Diamonds
description: Diamonds. They are forever. Dive into the arpeggiotron of Mord Fustang with this fresh set of grooves and atmospheres.

name: Pachet muzical | Michael Bross, Invasion!
description: Michael Bross conjures epic / cinematic techno-grunge to make you feel like a true badass in battle.

name: Pachet muzical | Ian Hultquist, Lion's Mouth
description: Mixing pulsating strings and synths with pounding war drums, prepare yourself for battle with this thunderous soundtrack from composer Ian Hultquist.

name: Pachet muzical | New Beat Fund, Sponge Fingerz
description: Sunny surf rock with elements of hip-hop, punk and garage pop. Keep it real and get headshots.

name: Pachet muzical | Beartooth, Disgusting
description: Beartooth brings an agressive back-to-basics hardcore stomp that gets crowds moving and breaking stuff. A perfect soundtrack for your no-scope scout frags. Rock 'till you're dead.

name: Pachet muzical | Lennie Moore, Java Havana Funkaloo
description: Game Composer Lennie Moore serves an aromatic, spicy blend of Jazzy Funk. Delicious when served cold, like the corpses of your enemies after you're done with them.

name: Pachet muzical | Darude, Moments CS:GO
description: Yield freely in the soundscapes of Finnish producer Darude's familiar musical flavours and tones. Enriching yourself with access to a heavy fusion of progressive overtones and scores of tingling melodic structure from the sounds banks of one of dance music's most renowned pioneers.

name: Pachet muzical | Beartooth, Aggressive
description: Beartooth revine pentru a doua rundă. Acest nou pachet muzical lovește și mai tare și este și mai agresiv. De asemenea, am făcut și imnul pentru MVP \"extra heavy\", astfel încât oponenții tăi să regrete din greu că au pierdut în fața ta.

name: Pachet muzical | Blitz Kids, The Good Youth
description: Formația Pop/Punk britanică Blitz Kids îți prezintă pachetul perfect muzical pentru un \"rush\" în B, în timp ce te gândești la plimbările nocturne pe care le-ai făcut cu prietenii din liceu. Acest pachet este creat pentru viteză și pentru a te face să te simți iarăși tânăr.

name: Pachet muzical | Hundredth, FREE
description: Hundredth reintroduce cuvântul \"heavy\" cu melodiile sale unice și \"hardcore\". Dă-ți frâu liber și revino în Dust cu această coloană sonoră perfectă pentru a-i frăgui pe cei nedemni.

name: Pachet muzical | Neck Deep, Life's Not Out To Get You
description: Uneori ai nevoie de niște muzică Pop Punk pentru a face față zilelor grele. Fie că ai de-a face cu pândari sau pierzi o serie masivă de ucideri, Neck Deep este aici pentru a arăta, prin melodia Life's Not Out To Get You, că viața nu îți vrea răul, spre deosebire de echipa adversă.

name: Pachet muzical | Roam, Backbone
description: Roam oferă Pop Punk rapid și direct, care pune în mișcare atât publicul, cât și jucătorii. Dovedește că ai coloană cu această coloană sonoră perfectă pentru o intrare rapidă și o nimicire a echipei adverse înainte ca oponenții să-și dea seama ce s-a întâmplat.

name: Pachet muzical | Twin Atlantic, GLA
description: Mai masivi, mai zgomotoși și mai răsunători ca oricând, Twin Atlantic vine în CS:GO pregătit să te ajute să distrugi adversarii cu puterea rockului scoțian.

name: Pachet muzical | Skog, III-Arena
description: Skog s-a întors cu al treilea set de muzică zdrobitoare metal. De această dată cu o poftă electro-organică pentru muzică, combinând riffurile masive de chitară cu dropurile la fel de masive, elementele în buclă și dronele.

name: Pachet muzical | The Verkkars, EZ4ENCE
description: The Verkkars rise through the Finnish charts with a heart-pounding tribute to ENCE. Can it really be so EZ?

name: Halo, The Master Chief Collection
description: Give your Counter Strike auditory experience a legendary makeover with the Master Chief Collection Music Pack, featuring iconic musical moments from the Halo universe. © 2019 343 Industries. All rights reserved. Used with permission from 343 Industries. Halo: The Master Chief Collection and the Halo logo are trademarks of the Microsoft group of companies.

name: Pachet muzical | Scarlxrd: King, Scar
description: Scarlxrd blends heavy trap beats with a flow and delivery that creates his own unique subgenre. With this exciting blend his live shows capture the attention of everyone in the crowd.

name: Half-Life: Alyx, Anti-Citizen
description: Acest pachet muzical comemorează Half-Life: Alyx, jocul prin care Valve revine în format RV la seria Half-Life. Tu ești ultima șansă de supraviețuire a omenirii și interacțiunile tale imersive în mediu continuă în Counter-Strike: Global Offensive.

name: Pachet muzical | Austin Wintory, Bachram
description: Austin Wintory mixes Celtic fantasy with sizzling electronics and a generous helping of Peter Hollens' vocals in this genre-bending Music Kit.

name: Pachet muzical | Dren, Gunman Taco Truck
description: The apocalyptic mariachi soundtrack from the indie game hit, Gunman Taco Truck, comes to CS:GO with intense Mexican flavored tunes like Pollo Diablo and Persecución de Helltain!

name: Pachet muzical | Daniel Sadowski, Eye of the Dragon
description: From the composer who brought you \"Total Domination\", \"The 8-Bit Kit\" and \"Crimson Assault\", comes \"Eye Of The Dragon\". Music composer Daniel Sadowski mixes Ninjas + Guns + Hip-Hop + Techno to create an action-packed Music Kit. Ninjas are known for their fast and precise attacks, yet they can be invisible to their enemy.

name: Pachet muzical | Tree Adams and Ben Bromfield, M.U.D.D. FORCE
description: Alchemists of a powerful chaos that is M.U.D.D. FORCE - composers Tree Adams and Ben Bromfield weld epic battle motifs and grinding synths into a Maelstrom of full throttle destruction.

name: Pachet muzical | Tim Huling, Neo Noir
description: Compozitorul Tim Huling ne oferă piese clasice specifice filmelor noir într-o compoziție cu ritmuri contemporane.

name: Pachet muzical | Sam Marshall, Bodacious
description: Inspirat de muzica jocurilor video funky de la începutul anilor '90, compozitorul Sam Marshall combină nostalgia jocurilor video clasice cu o notă modernă.

name: Pachet muzical | Matt Levine, Drifter
description: Composer Matt Levine delivers raw swagger in this gritty homage to the Spaghetti Western. It has never felt better to say, \"go ahead, make my day...\"

name: Pachet muzical | Amon Tobin, All for Dust
description: Legendary producer Amon Tobin lends his unique aesthetic to CS:GO. This time through tube amplifiers.

name: Darren Korb, Hades
description: Sure, you might miss a shot from time to time, but what never misses is this blood-pumping Music Kit straight from the Underworld of Hades, Supergiant's rogue-like dungeon crawler.

name: Pachet muzical | Neck Deep, The Lowlife Pack
description: Prove you are not a normie (and better than everyone else on the map) with Neck Deep's new music kit, which includes songs from the band's album All Distortions Are Intentional.

name: Pachet muzical | Scarlxrd, CHAIN$AW.LXADXUT.
description: CHAIN$AW BRINGS SCARLXRD AT HIS UNPRECENDENTED BEST WITH A RAW FLOW AND A HEAVY TRACK TO MATCH.

name: Pachet muzical | Austin Wintory, Mocha Petal
description: Austin Wintory answers the question humanity has asked for ages: what happens if you merge beer garden accordion polka music with grungy heavy metal?

name: Pachet muzical | Chipzel, ~Yellow Magic~
description: Video game composer and chiptune legend Chipzel brings a glitchy Speak & Spell inspired mashup of hybrid styles packed with fun, funk and flavour.

name: Pachet muzical | Freaky DNA, Vici
description: Opera. 8-bit sounds. Analogue synths. What's not to love? Chiptune specialist Freaky DNA and soprano Leanne Koch team up for some heavy beats and good times!

name: Pachet muzical | Jesse Harlin, Astro Bellum
description: Composer Jesse Harlin delivers bombastic space opera drama inspired by classic sci-fi of the 70s, 80s, and beyond.

name: Pachet muzical | Laura Shigihara: Work Hard, Play Hard
description: Video game composer and developer Laura Shigihara will help you tell everyone loudly and proudly that you're the MVP. Have fun with this unique blend of 90s dance, retro video game synth, and just a hint of Plants vs. Zombies.

name: Pachet muzical | Sarah Schachner, KOLIBRI
description: Brought to you by Sarah Schachner, a dystopian goth choir of self-aware, Scandinavian robots decide that humanity must be eliminated.

name: Pachet muzical | bbno$, u mad!
description: bbno$ formulates 'the' toxic gamer anthem, u mad! Are u mad? LOL get good scrub. Research shows if you play with this Music Kit equipped you'll immediately go from Silver to Global.

name: Pachet muzical | The Verkkars & n0thing, Flashbang Dance
description: From sunny California to frigid Lapland, Counter-Strike legend n0thing and The Verkkars combine powers to create the smash hit, Flashbang Dance! 3, 2, 1 you’re blind!

name: Pachet muzical | 3kliksphilip, Heading for the Source
description: Ești pe cale să devii un profesionist sau te afli într-un declin neintenționat? Lasă acest pachet muzical cu sintetizatoare din anii '80 și caractere melodice de vis să te poarte înapoi. Mult, mult înapoi... în vremurile bune de odinioară.

name: Pachet muzical | Humanity's Last Breath, Void
description: Trupa suedeză Humanity's Last Breath vine în forță cu pachetul muzical Void. Tobe puternice, riffuri colosale și o atmosferă care îți dă fiori pe șira spinării.

name: Pachet muzical | Juelz, Shooters
description: Sintetizatoare neo trap, 808-uri de înaltă calitate, un riff de pian epic și o multitudine de efecte sonore de împușcături. Imnul OG trap „Shooters” al lui Juelz face ca acest pachet muzical să fie unul de elită. Perfect doar pentru MVP-uri.

name: Pachet muzical | Knock2, dashstar*
description: dashstar*, imnul emblematic bass house al lui Knock2, oferă o energie nelimitată care surprinde mantra tinerilor din San Diego, „fără limite”.

name: Pachet muzical | Meechy Darko, Gothic Luxury
description: Ia un Glock, echipează pachetul acesta muzical și lasă-te purtat de scena underground hip-hop din New York.

name: Pachet muzical | Sullivan King, Lock Me Up
description: Îți place vânătoare și procesul de urmărire al prăzii? Genurile hard rock, metal și dubstep se contopesc în această coloană sonoră a lui Sullivan King concepută pentru a deveni de neoprit.

name: Pachet muzical | Perfect World, 花脸 Hua Lian (Painted Face)
description: Sărbătorește cea de-a 5-a aniversare de la lansarea jocului CS:GO în China cu un pachet muzical unic, 花脸 Hua Lian (Painted Face). Acest pachet muzical îmbină elementele de operă folk Qinqiang (cel mai timpuriu stil chinezesc de Rock ‘n’ Roll) cu elementele moderne de Rock ‘n’ Roll. Fie că ești surprins de fumul unei grenade fumigene sau orbit de către o grenadă de șoc, nu-ți pierde simțul orientării!

name: Pachet muzical | Denzel Curry, ULTIMATE
description: Denzel brings his signature energy to CS:GO as he traverses trap, jazz, and drum and bass beats. This kit features Denzel's hits \"Walkin\", \"ULTIMATE\", and more, so break out the nickel-plated chrome Berettas and crank up the intensity with the ULTIMATE music kit.
